  "translations": {
    "en": "And know you, O slaves of Allah! Together with this there will be mercy of Allah which will not be thwarted from the slaves – a Paradise as wide as the heavens and the earth, prepared for those who fear Allah. Good with no evil accompanying it at any time; its pleasures will never be satiated and its gathering will never disperse. Its inmates will be in proximity of the Merciful, attended by youths with golden saucers containing fruits and sweet basils.",
